snippet.title: The Sims 4 Parenthood: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Develop your Sim’s parenting skills to help shape their children’s lives into adulthood with The Sims 4 Parenthood.

Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/30907 
What kind of parent will you be? Take the quiz: http://x.ea.com/30906 

Choose when to discipline or encourage child behaviors, teach life values, and leave a lasting impact on their future. Experience fun family activities and personalize your household with new home décor and family fashion.

“Don’t Kill My Vibe” (Simlish Version) performed by Sigrid
